graph TB
    subgraph Sidecar["llm-d-routing-sidecar (Go HTTP Reverse Proxy)"]
        direction TB
        Proxy["Reverse Proxy<br/>Port 8000/TCP<br/>HTTP or HTTPS"]
        NIXLv2["NIXL v2 Connector<br/>(default protocol)"]
        NIXLv1["NIXL v1 Connector<br/>(deprecated)"]
        LMCache["LMCache Connector<br/>(deprecated)"]
        Allowlist["AllowlistValidator<br/>SSRF Protection"]
        TLSMgr["TLS Manager<br/>Self-signed or cert-path"]
        LRUCache["LRU Proxy Cache<br/>Capacity: 16"]

        Proxy -->|selects protocol| NIXLv2
        Proxy -->|selects protocol| NIXLv1
        Proxy -->|selects protocol| LMCache
        Proxy -->|validates target| Allowlist
        Proxy -->|TLS termination| TLSMgr
        Proxy -->|caches handlers| LRUCache
    end

    Client["Client / EPP"] -->|POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>x-prefiller-host-port header| Proxy
    Client -->|POST /v1/completions| Proxy
    Client -->|GET /health| Proxy

    Proxy -->|decode requests| LocalDecoder["Local vLLM Decoder<br/>localhost:8001/TCP"]
    NIXLv2 -->|prefill requests<br/>kv_transfer_params| RemotePrefiller["Remote vLLM Prefiller<br/>variable port/TCP"]
    NIXLv1 -->|prefill requests<br/>do_remote_prefill| RemotePrefiller
    LMCache -->|prefill requests<br/>max_tokens=1| RemotePrefiller

    Allowlist -->|watches| InferencePool["InferencePool CR<br/>inference.networking.x-k8s.io"]
    Allowlist -->|watches pod IPs| K8sPods["Kubernetes Pods<br/>matching pool selectors"]

    Scheduler["llm-d-inference-scheduler<br/>(EPP)"] -->|sets x-prefiller-host-port| Client

    style Proxy fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style NIXLv2 fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style NIXLv1 fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style LMCache fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Allowlist fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style TLSMgr fill:#f39c12,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style LRUCache fill:#3498db,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style LocalDecoder fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style RemotePrefiller fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style InferencePool fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style K8sPods fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Scheduler fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Client fill:#ecf0f1,stroke:#333
